d":222970,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"每個中國人都可以成為楊佳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/6/18/n10495037.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F6%2F18%2Fn10495037.htm&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=df53422d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/6/18/n10495037.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2008年7月的一天，北京青年楊佳持刀殺死六名上海閘北公安分局警察，四個月後被執行死刑。楊佳殺警後，在民間引起驚濤駭浪，網絡上卻是一片支持聲浪。楊佳一句「你不給我一個說法， 我就給你一個說法」，引發前所未有的共鳴。<br />\n<br />\n據媒體報導稱，2007年楊佳在上海火車站租了一輛自行車，被警方認為涉嫌購買贓車，以盜竊罪名將其拘留。在這期間，楊佳遭遇警方暴打，他的性器官受到損害，造成可能無法生育的後果。<br />\n<br />\n閘北分局同意賠償1500元人民幣私了此事，楊佳不能接受，他又多次到警局討說法，警局不理不睬，並對楊佳進行威脅、恐嚇。於是發生殺警案，導致六名警察死亡、三名警察和一名保安受傷，楊佳當場被捕。"},{"pid":"5f96d8ad2263372520d1bca5178346f283758408","tid":2196053,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68edf99c6c3ea84fbda4db622e5f76762679fe67","tid":2196053,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"好耐啦條片"},{"pid":"df5773a99e817552ff131fd7857e1fafed462ea4","tid":2196053,"uid":36134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"68edf99c6c3ea84fbda4db622e5f76762679fe67","tid":2196053,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"好耐啦條片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"有無英文版先 無既再耐都要推到有英文"},{"pid":"b505adb54b48a24872e9b3fed949da7f1a69aab2","tid":2196053,"uid":253354,"like":1,"dislike":129,"score":-128,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:15:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾温和，下下都踢背脊，應該踢頭 ！"},{"pid":"66ac48c0b0d5c856cdde75aae0aabf4b1fddddd1","tid":2196053,"uid":9542,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"b505adb54b48a24872e9b3fed949da7f1a69aab2","tid":2196053,"uid":253354,"like":1,"dislike":129,"score":-128,"ci