脅、恐嚇。於是發生殺警案，導致六名警察死亡、三名警察和一名保安受傷，楊佳當場被捕。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:01:09.000Z","msg":"上海楊桂殺警案<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">楊佳母親<span class=\"x-large\">被失蹤</span>送往<ins>精神病院</ins></span><br />\n之後拍成電影 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QdqfzaC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQdqfzaC.png&h=5682f2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCBuDEm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCBuDEm.png&h=eac56ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uJXNxH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1uJXNxH.png&h=90783ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">【女屍赤裸是很大疑點】想屈彥霖冇戴 bra ?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194298</a><br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T18:19:30.000Z","msg":"其實共產黨最驚唔係外國勢力/港獨台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係國內既無產階級重拾當年毛主席教落無產階級鬥爭，講到尾就係同你鬥爛命，到時九千萬黨員再加軍隊都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e4f6a16ba314d12e456d85c9bdb6732b28744b","tid":2196053,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0931289db269d4e3ad11cf18aca7915416b32e","tid":2196053,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ee457f889c5d716bb2510ccd43436fbcb56f07","tid":2196053,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8334f884f9b9f8531eb34c17c6358549327fa05a","tid":2196053,"uid":82752,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"嬲完 第日好準時返工啦 奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:35:54.000Z","msg":"嬲完就要武裝打佢老母咩古代人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:37:26.000Z","msg":"現階段連嬲都唔敢/忘記 就真係連藍絲d單細胞生物都不如<